ets-is-no-more&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199965/the-netflix-app-for-quest-headsets-is-no-more" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199965/the-netflix-app-for-quest-headsets-is-no-more</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:17:25-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:17:25-04:00</updated><title> Ozy Media 创始人卡洛斯·沃森犯有欺诈罪</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2017 年活动期间，戴着墨镜的凯蒂·库里克 (Katie Couric) 站在卡洛斯·沃森 (Carlos Watson) 旁边，站在写着“Ozy Fest”的标牌前。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hOBSFbkgjljFSot0arxE4s4gRDI=/804x0:4550x2497/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464656/820900644.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption >;Katie Couric（左）和 Ozy 首席执行官兼联合创始人 Carlos Watson 在 2017 年 Ozy Fest 期间登台演讲 |摄影：Bryan Bedder/Getty Images for Ozy Fusion Fest 2017&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;O4p5Vx&quot;>;Carlos Watson 和他共同创立的现已关闭的 Ozy Media 初创公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .justice.gov/usao-edny/pr/carlos-watson-Founder-and-former-ceo-ozy-media-inc-convicted-multi-million-dollar&quot;>;被联邦法院判定犯有欺诈罪&lt;/a>;周二陪审团，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/07/16/business/media/carlos-watson-ozy-media-guilty.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;amp; referingSource=articleShare&amp;amp;sgrp=c-cb&quot;>;《纽约时报》早些时候报道过&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。在长达数周的审判过程中，陪审团听取了政府的指控，即 Ozy Media 通过伪造财务记录、夸大观众人数，甚至捏造商业交易来误导投资者。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3jGyq6&quot; >;Ozy Media 前首席执行官沃森 (Watson) 于 2013 年与萨米尔·拉奥 (Samir Rao) 共同创立了该公司。该公司推出了在线杂志、时事通讯，并在纽约市举办了年度会议，同时达成了高调的合作伙伴关系和 &lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fmoney%2Fbusiness%2F2014%2F10%2F06%2Faxel-springer-investment- in-ozy%2F16764657%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F16%2F24199947%2Fozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;获得数百万&lt;/a>;投资。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1yJofV&quot;>;但是当 2021 年 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.nytimes.com/2021/09/26/business/media/ozy-media-goldman-sachs.html&quot;>;来自《纽约时报》的文章&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/ em>;媒体专栏作家本·史密斯...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty -fraud&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:11:05-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:11:05-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的降噪耳机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一对黑色索尼 WH-1000XM5 耳机，平放在笔记本电脑旁边的木桌上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1Yi9sFXnZ3b-FYYS4HNbyWq5zLc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67126629/DSCF7916.15.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;索尼 WH-1000XM5 耳机采用全新设计。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;使用我们精选的任何一款降噪耳机，享受宁静与安宁。总体而言，索尼仍然是最好的，但也有理由去其他地方。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21345733/best-noise-canceling-headphones&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21345733/best-noise-canceling-headphones" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21345733/best-noise-canceling-headphones</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:05:24-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:05:24-04:00</updated><title>您可以乘坐虚拟火车逃离皇家加勒比游轮</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;皇家铁路乌托邦车站沉浸式火车体验餐厅的渲染效果。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eybU9N5DRVmNlLUGAohT0bJa_6Y=/0x1:1430x954/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464638/royal_caribbean_cruise_train1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;在海洋乌托邦号上，您可以体验火车用餐，没有颠簸和饮料溢出。&lt;/em>; |图片：皇家加勒比&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ndphdP&quot;>;新的 5,668 名乘客&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.royalcaribbean.com/utopia-of-the-seas/&quot;>;皇家加勒比海洋乌托邦号停靠在佛罗里达州，那里有&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url= 等网站&lt;em>; &lt;/em>; https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cruisecritic.com%2Fnews%2Fa-train-at-sea-royal-caribbean-lays-the-tracks-for-new-dining-experience&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https% 3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F16%2F24199880%2Froyal-caribbean-utopia-of-the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt; em>;Cruise Critic&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 在 7 月 19 日投入服务之前已经预览了这些设施。其中包括名为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.royalcaribbean.com/cruise-dining/royal-railway-utopia-station&quot;>;皇家铁路乌托邦站&lt;/a>;的独特体验，乘客可以在虚拟火车上用餐一边乘坐，一边盯着大屏幕上飞驰而过的模拟风景。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WJDa2G&quot;>;这家餐厅看起来像两辆全尺寸的有轨电车，内饰豪华，两侧排列着四人包厢，每个都有自己的巨型显示屏作为虚拟窗口。食客从这些虚拟窗口看到的东西将全年轮换。第一个体验是西部主题，可以看到山脉、峡谷和淘金小镇的景色。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;Cx2VA2&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;位置：相对；padding-bottom：56.25%;&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Ro3Pbo&quot;>;&lt;q>;谋杀在...&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of -the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of-the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199880/royal-caribbean-utopia-of-the-seas-cruise-trains-immersive</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:02:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:02:54-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的无线耳机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 WF-1000XM5 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e6t1Ea8VCnt9pPlNtEqC2_bCfCc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67005648/DSCF2232.22.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;来自 Apple、Bose、三星、索尼、Beats、Google 等的最佳产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:00:50-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:00:50-04:00</updated><title> 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳智能手表和健身追踪器优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉红色系列 9 位于反光粉红色表面上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9DHeQLb64Xb3trWBGEIRg9dhnc0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73463591/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_090 2.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple Watch 和大量 Android 智能手表在 Prime Day 期间打折。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;25TTLK&quot;>;2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 即将到来，随之而来的是 Apple Watch、Android 智能手表甚至只是普通的健身追踪器。秋季产品发布即将到来，但如果您的预算有限，现在是获得更高品质材料和去年优质设备折扣的好时机。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;dmSlfd&quot;>;浏览数千种交易可能会很痛苦，尤其是当您考虑到数十种智能手表型号、尺寸、颜色和材料时。不用担心——我们已经为您做到了这一点，并汇总了最优惠的价格。 （只需确保您拥有 Prime 会员资格即可访问它们！）当您检查完智能手表和健身追踪器后，您可以返回我们的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/amazon- prime-day-deals-tech&quot;>;Prime Day 优惠主页面&lt;/a>;了解更多信息。 &lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;zdApaN&quot;>;一个...&lt;/h2>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199083/amazon-prime- day-2024-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;